room_title: Escape room "Area 51" by HD Escape Rooms Westminster in Denver
room_description: In 1947, an unidentified object crashed outside of Roswell, New Mexico. The U.S. Government wasted no time in establishing a classified base known as Area 51, surrounding the crash site and preventing any knowledge from leaking, but now the secrets have come to our escape room so those in the Westminster area can finally learn the truth of the autopsies and experiments that have taken place since the first event in Roswell. Combine your intelligence with others to see if you can find your way out. Check out our Westminster alien autopsy escape room when youâ€™re ready for an adventure.
